		{
			"id":"30ad9aa264d099a8",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"**【具体例子】**\n- 包管理：npm、yarn、pnpm、bun\n- 脚手架工具：create-vue、create-next-app、create-react-touter\n- 转义与编译：Babel、TSC、PostCSS、Oxc Transformer\n- 构建与打包：Rspack、Vite、SWC、ESBuild、Oxc Rolldown\n- 开发服务器：Dev Server\n- 代码质量工具：ESLint、Prettier、Biome、Oxc Lint\n- 测试工具：Vitest、Jest、Cypress、Playwright、Lighthouse",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":2500,
			"y":660,
			"width":580,
			"height":270
		},
